summary: A player is changed into lovely voice.
descriptionHtml:

SAMPLE VIDEO
------------------------------
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4NkpR0axFw

-----------------------------
INTRODUCTION 
-----------------------------
A player is changed into lovely voice. 
(some voice is share similarity with NPC)

-----Player voice changed. \\\"Only female human\\\" ------
- Usual attack 
- Power attack 
- Power attack (stamina low)
- Get damage
- Death
- Breath when running (stamina low,mid,max)
- Breath when no stamina
- Eagle eye (hold breath, blow out a breath)
- Breath out of the water


-----Player voice which is not changed -------------------
- Dragon shout
- Shield power bussh 
- When a shield receives an attack 
- When stamina residual quantity is extremely low and it defends with a shield

------------------------------
ABOUT OPTIONAL FILE
------------------------------
If you like Nya-! shout (Throw Voice shout) .
Download a main file and an option file.
